{"tid":1674875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[後果自負]空運牌照局促香港航空短期內改善財政　否則或採取行動","createTime":"2019-10-25T13:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T14:28:18.000Z","uid":51271,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b4d908f3ae1c67f706760b81013dad7ec5bc1c15","tid":1674875,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"空運牌照局開會後決定，要求香港航空立即採取實際行動，短期內有效地改善財政狀況。否則，牌照局會按情況考慮根據《空運（航空服務牌照）規例》採取適當的行動。<br />\n<br />\n空運牌照局說，有鑑於香港航空持續出現的財政問題，牌照過去一段長時間一直密切審視該公司的情況，並多次根據《規例》，要求香港航空向牌照局提交財政改善計劃。<br />\n<br />\n牌照局在考慮香港航空最近提交的資料後，認為香港航空目前的財政問題依然未有改善跡象，情況令人關注。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488260-20191025.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488260-20191025.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTXG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=adbfa120\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488260-20191025.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4f68f9fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488260-20191025.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"606f33ffa676bf04e10d60d35c18305aa6a739b9","tid":1674875,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:36:47.000Z","msg":"真係攬炒成功"},{"pid":"d7b1447dd5cd3eacf96e457242ba3954a74c2100","tid":1674875,"uid":53876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"上年已經話過唔掂喎"},{"pid":"d12b80c5c67b71fdcff11a3547de7514a6c6335a","tid":1674875,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"